{"tid":1646333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-10-11T09:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T14:02:39.000Z","uid":41873,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1c28dc48dceeb6660afa4a5e789a58fd51f1ddc5","tid":1646333,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">[文長，但希望你會花兩分鐘去睇同推]</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個post 我希望大家可以一人盡一下力 令到可以置頂<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">直至完全成功爭取五大訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無錯 連登已經俾好多不知明人士入侵左 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢個大家都好清楚係政府既招數</span></span></strong> 目的係乜唔多講啦 有腦既人都會知<br />\n<br />\n我相信大家亦都知我地今次一輸 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會再有贏既一日</span></span></strong>，所以所有香港人，我相信你地既<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">理念，信念，盼望</span></span></strong>都係一樣，如果唔係大家都唔會走到黎呢一步，正正係因為大家既<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">團結，互相扶持，</span></span></strong>先會令到我覺得今次我地會贏，亦都成為我今次開呢個post既原因<br />\n<br />\n緊記，香港人，要贏就<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要團結，齊上齊落，不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆</span></span></strong>，每次檢討過後就要繼續努力，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，Be Water, Be Smart</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我文筆唔好，希望各位見諒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，反抗！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9e351edab5df26cf390811d6f289966c7b79d9b1","tid":1646333,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e62da99051d61dae63ea295db58aaae01f9b37ff","tid":1646333,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09